
HACBS Enterprise Contract Documentation
=======================================

About
-----

The HACBS Enterprise Contract is a Tekton task that can be used to verify the
provenence of a container image built in HACBS and validate it against a set of
policies.

The policies are defined in
[rego](https://www.openpolicyagent.org/docs/latest/policy-language/) and are
described here.

